media:group.media:title: Kerbal Scuffed Program 2 | Jeb is dead (and we killed him)
media:group.media:description:
Welcome back, today we're playing KSP once again. In this instalment, our Kerbals journey beyond the confines of Kerbin's gravity to the great beyond. (Duna). Many more Kerbals were harmed in the making of this video.
